ji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nUp咩</blockquote><br />\n教育局既提議簡單直接，唔通下下長篇大論教人點抽絲剝繭理解自殺者心態咩，又唔係要教你點做輔導，就算佢真係講得好複雜詳盡，到時又有邊個有心睇。唔洗下下奉政府必反既。"},{"pid":"8bc7a320a419074206693dbffa1e6cf30039667d","tid":187394,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:48:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31509db0ec2d344ab48f1d4d0046bd2031d8837b","tid":187394,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:48:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發撚癲<br />\n自殺嘅人最撚憎聽人講埋啲理性野<br />\n例如: 死解決唔到問題  唔好咁傻<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母我想解決問題就唔撚會想死啦  我係傻  咁我咪死囉仲想點撚樣<br />\n<br />\n明報呢個報導證明政府班冚家剷真係害人精嚟</blockquote><br />\n其實你有無上果個網睇下，定只係鳩噏緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd86fee2a2fa72daa27cdfbe486653909b926bc","tid":187394,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:50:31.000Z","msg":"據我所知係香港男仔為情自殺好似多過女仔囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94212a4ccf3e5a311b7609a0416f68352c6a2908","tid":187394,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:50:50.000Z","msg":"終於有啲貼地啲嘅說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f140c7628991d68911c182a7cead1b3b8e1d734","tid":187394,"uid":100861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:51:51.000Z","msg":"學生不應談戀愛"},{"pid":"4dae4d91b1d8a5655f3595dd8fb398763bff26ed","tid":187394,"uid":30794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:52:31.000Z","msg":"冇男/女朋友咁點？"},{"pid":"4e0cb076f08d104979831650d8921608d7f23c08","tid":187394,"uid":32006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:52:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗調返轉男女就差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n女團: 告你性別歧視"},{"pid":"d1cebd09d708f05c1c2081d3d41241db6fc1c231","tid":187394,"uid":6799,"like"